com.percussion.loader.ui
Interface IPSExtractorConfigChangeListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
PSItemExtractorConfigPanel
public interface IPSExtractorConfigChangeListener

This interface may be implemented by one of the sub-panels within a configuration panel of a extractor. It is used to listen for PSExtractorConfigChangeEvent fired by certain tab panels.

See Also:
IPSExtractorConfigTabPanel, PSAbstractExtractorConfigTabPanel

Method Summary
 void configChanged(PSExtractorConfigChangeEvent event)
          This method is called when a configuration change occurs for the extractor tab panel that this listener is registered to.
